(37, 5, 17, NULL, 3, 22, 65, 'Dell SE2419H 24 Inch IPS LCD Monitor', '<h2>Dell SE2419H 24 Inch 60Hz IPS LCD Monitor</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>No matter where you sit, colours stay accurate and consistent across the wide 178&deg;/178&deg; viewing angle thanks to in-plane switching technology. No matter where you sit, colours stay accurate and consistent across the wide 178&deg;/178&deg; viewing angle thanks to in-plane switching technology. The stand is now 30% smaller, freeing up desk space without compromising sturdiness. A built-in power supply unit further reduces clutter. Easily tilt the monitor to get just the right viewing angle. Protect your eyes by minimizing harmful blue light with Dell&rsquo;s ComfortView feature. Optimize eye comfort and minimize distractions thanks to a flicker-free, anti-glare screen. Stay organized between applications, emails and windows on one screen using Dell Easy Arrange. Our products are engineered with care and precision, so you are guaranteed support and peace of mind. As the No. 1 monitor brand worldwide , we take pride in our unyielding commitment to quality and the utmost satisfaction of our customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What is the price of Dell SE2419H 24 Inch LCD Monitor in Bangladesh?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The latest price of Dell SE2419H 24 Inch LCD Monitor in Bangladesh is 15,900৳. You can buy the Dell SE2419H 24 Inch LCD Monitor at best price from our website or visit any of our showrooms.</p>', '<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\">Display Features</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Panel Type</td>\r\n			<td>In-Plane switching (IPS) Technology</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Screen Size</td>\r\n			<td>23.5 Inch</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Display Type</td>\r\n			<td>LED-backlit LCD monitor</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Resolution</td>\r\n			<td>Full HD (1080p): 1920 x 1080 at 60 Hz</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Brigh