(41, 5, 17, NULL, 3, 22, 65, 'Dell S2419HGF 24\" 144Hz Gaming Monitor', '<p>Smooth gameplay: Experience sharp, tear-free graphics with a swift refresh rate at 144Hz and AMD FreeSync for super smooth visuals. Leave lag behind: Get blazing fast and responsive gameplay with minimum input lag at an extremely rapid 1ms response time. If looks could thrill: Recon-blue metallic finishing complements Dell Gaming PCs for a unified look and gaming experience. Total versatility: Supports AMD FreeSync&trade; and offers you the flexibility to game with the No-Sync fast refresh option on your existing hardware. Customize your advantage: Personalize and preset up to three gaming profiles, in addition to three factory preset modes, with a gamer-geared menu. Made to game your way: With tilt, pivot, swivel and height adjustable features, you can find your ideal viewing position and game for long hours comfortably. Effortless Connectivity: With the wide range of ports, hook up this Gaming Monitor to your PC, and add another secondary device &ndash; like your gaming console of choice &ndash; for simultaneous entertainment options.</p>', '<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\">Display Features</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Panel Type</td>\r\n			<td>TN</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Screen Size</td>\r\n			<td>24&quot;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Display Type</td>\r\n			<td>LED-backlit LCD monitor</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Resolution</td>\r\n			<td>Full HD (1080p) 1920 x 1080 at 144 Hz</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Brightness</td>\r\n			<td>350 cd/m2 (typical)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Response Time</td>\r\n			<td>1ms (gray to gray)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Viewing Angle</td>\r\n			<td>178&deg; vertical / 178&deg; horizontal</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Contrast Ratio</td>\r\n			<td>1000: 1 (Typical), 8 Million: 1 (Dynamic)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\