(71, 5, 18, NULL, 3, 23, 65, 'HP V194 18.5 inch LED Backlight Monitor', '<p>HP V194 18.5 inch LED Backlight Monitor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quality presentation features at a price point that doesn&rsquo;t break the bank with the HP V194 18.5-inch Monitor, a sleek, thinprofile monitor in a compact, space-saving screen size with an unbelievably low price point.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Enjoy crisp, clear views of your documents and e-mail with 1366 x 768 resolution, 5M:1 dynamic contrast ratio, and 5 ms response time on an 18.5-inch diagonal screen.1 Quickly and easily connect to your devices with a VGA input.</li>\r\n	<li>Mount your HP Desktop Mini 2602 directly behind the display for an integrated, affordable workspace that&rsquo;s perfect for small spaces. Or, use the integrated VESA mount to place the display on a wall or stand.2</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce power consumption and help lower your costs with an intelligent, energy-efficient design that is ENERGY STAR&reg; certified and EPEAT&reg; Silver registered.3 The display also includes mercury-free display backlights and arsenic-free display glass.</li>\r\n	<li>Customize your display&rsquo;s position with adjustable tilt settings and viewing angles.</li>\r\n	<li>Rest assured that your IT investment is supported by a three-year standard limited warranty. To extend your protection, select optional HP Care Packs.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Warranty 3 Years (parts)</p>', '<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\">MONITOR</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Screen Size</td>\r\n			<td>18.5&quot;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Contrast Ratio</td>\r\n			<td>Typical-600:1 II<br />\r\n			Dynamic- 5,000,000:1 II</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Response Time</td>\r\n			<td>5 ms (on/off)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Resolution</td>\r\n			<td>1366 x 768 at 60 Hz</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Connectivity</td>\r