(342, 30, 31, NULL, 3, 35, 65, 'Transcend 220S 240GB 2.5 Inch SATAIII SSD', '<h2>Transcend 220S 240GB 2.5 Inch SATAIII SSD</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Transcend 220S SSD comes with 240GB capacity. Here uses the latest 3D NAND technology that features with vertical, stacked expansion of storage cells. By using high-quality flash memory and enhanced firmware algorithms, the SSD220S delivers greater performance and reliability. The 3D NAND overcomes density limitations of 2D planar NAND, and delivers a higher level of performance and endurance. Here 3D NAND flash features memory cells stacked vertically in multiple layers. Transcend&#39;s SSD220S achieves exceptional transfer speeds of up to 550MB/s read and 500MB/s write and built-in SLC caching technology. This SSD dominate the market for PC upgrades because they are faster and lighter than hard disk drives. SSDs also feature less power, create less noise when in operation, and are more shock-resistant than traditional hard drives. It measures just 6.8mm in height and features short access times, making it a perfect choice for upgrading desktops, laptops, and the latest gaming consoles in just 3 easy steps. The Transcend&rsquo;s solid state drives are built to the highest standards and rigorously tested, and offer outstanding quality, performance, and reliability. This SSD 220S comes with 03 years of warranty.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What is the price of Transcend 220S 240GB SSD in Bangladesh?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The latest price of Transcend 220S 240GB SSD in Bangladesh is 3,850৳. You can buy the Transcend 220S 240GB SSD at best price from our website or visit any of our showrooms.</p>', '<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\">Key Features</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Capacity</td>\r\n			<td>240GB</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Form Factor</td>\r\n			<td>2.5&quot;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Flash Type</td>\r\n			<td>3D NAND flash</td>\r\n		</tr>\r