(361, 30, 31, NULL, 3, 35, 65, 'Transcend 370S 256GB 2.5\" SATA SSD', '<p>Transcend&#39; SATA III 6Gb/s SSD370S boasts incredibly fast transfer speeds, MLC NAND flash memory, a compact and lightweight design, and shock and vibration resistance. With this solid state drive, you will enjoy a seamless, lag-free computing experience.Transcend&#39;s SSD370S is manufactured with reliable, top-tier MLC NAND flash memory to ensure superior stability and endurance, making it well-suited to high-end applications.Taking full advantage of the SATA III 6Gb/s interface, DDR3 DRAM cache and a powerful controller, Transcend&#39;s SSD370S delivers blazing-fast read and write speeds of up to 560MB/s and 460MB/s.ranscend&#39;s SSD370S measures just 6.8mm in height and features short access times, making it a perfect choice for upgrading desktops, laptops, and the latest gaming consoles in just 3 easy steps!</p>', '<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\">Key Features</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Capacity</td>\r\n			<td>256GB</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Form Factor</td>\r\n			<td>2.5&quot;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Flash Type</td>\r\n			<td>3D NAND</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Interface</td>\r\n			<td><br />\r\n			SATA III 6Gb/s</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Sequential R/W</td>\r\n			<td>Read Speed (Max.) 560 MB/s<br />\r\n			Write Speed (Max.) 500 MB/s</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\">Physical Specification</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Dimension (L x W x H)</td>\r\n			<td>42.0 mm x 22.0 mm x 3.58 mm (1.65&quot; x 0.87&quot; x 0.14&quot;)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Weight</td>\r\n			<td>6 g (0.21 oz)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\">Temperature</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Operating Temperature</td>\r\n			<td>0&deg;C (32&