(692, 1, 2, 50, 3, 53, 65, 'Thermaltake Versa H27 Tempered Glass Side Window Mid Tower Black Gaming Desktop Case # CA-1J6-00M1WN-00', '<h2>Thermaltake Versa H27</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/HpEprZdRr4Wkpaztffkq6HuZUKhenxBuSFgTV3db5T5YIJQP2GahLPxnvms8xwMcOwuvmYHjGP8EWoXvdz76CxIeYdlBTH7TzhyBET4uSftL0VvYI200n_9MRZ-_7dCf-2IDLgex\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Thermaltake Versa H27 Tempered Glass Edition Mid-Tower Chassis</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/RXlfn65WVj6oG-YfNYC31WE0ttYCnsLqIsvwsttg98j84ZsDhORC_BvG6I74ENBH9oUIQuOfZspIJwlG5Qx_mLFDDjGRLilVXCvc6qiq1gv_1HHHfJnAjfIuxmApOjM9ntfH1g4m\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Designed for entry-level PC builders and gamers, Thermaltake Versa H27 Tempered Glass Edition Mid-Tower Chassis features a durable 4mm thick tempered glass window, excellent expandability with easy cable management design, AIO liquid cooling compatible and ample ventilation options. Supporting the latest PC hardware and all high-end GPU solutions, the Versa H27 TG is a good choice for those who opt for a budget-friendly PC case with manageable frame size and advanced features.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>4mm Thick Left Tempered Glass Window Design</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ndWz2dk9GGGaXwm4Z6qWv2zYDI8T8XefH0h-giFImeTwQS4BvcwlE__QjitRBFW7QnkZ89xVaYioEZd5halRwtwGC8tWKRXyUqVvmcv5R5ZA9zhLBOVkW8MR66EBxFm3PrYADqrx\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 4mm thick left tempered glass panel guarantees the durability of the window and display your build with crisp clarity.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Built for Gamers</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/y1lc2DzHXasA4MkFtuby2n7CfPpj7hbd_EffTQrPq8_vuKbNy15gIcSimpsRdoNR82o6nMHye1Aal_ulEUSPp6mfztK9GAXUyQBTlPx1U-qNHhEXwpSL2zLgAHZdwIxZ4z0BcAQR\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The enlarged glass window with full metal front panel allows users to display all component of the build, offering a direct view of inner system. The perforated top panel plus the heighted foot-stands at the bottom provide efficient airflow for the system.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Handy I/O Ports</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/m5LX3ChbkpBcS0KUqyjelJls0zXZi2RaD0WVsgAvD3flcu5Snj3Yo3snGNAkSXZE9jPRBaE0Ck3TRY6MV-zF1R3XzXLtZWguL5I-HU8kfSHAT_Dyq6IX4aS2XDtm8NKqsqngiXVt\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The front panel is designed two USB 3.0 data transfer ports along with two standard USB 2.0 ports and a HD microphone and headset jacks, to grand direct access when needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Easy Cable Management</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/1NPBt_X59JGv3BDDVWFYiePWPnNciyz9Ig30KHqIoVvxJAEUqhlROSmvvZIjVTAHYazDVNObuZ6IXMS0k1omSwvrDwZI7WtomKtpeYJ_cJgo2nhtyZDIjAaCWxrc-HkQT6untX5C\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wiring tangled problem no longer exists with the cable routing gap, hiding cables behind motherboard tray to ensure smoothness for building the system as well as better airflow. Plus, the pre-mounted PSU cover allows the entire bottom area of the case to be used to reorganize unused cables.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Superior Hardware Support</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/eYFasRfcZVmRndAb12SNQTKtuq__kcq4gz-SbzxgWUpcXsb1TSwmdbyh1IUkGiRJ9Gy9voOx-UjnvOnx3L2p_MnvVe1LgxMMX9oqvI0W_IYHSfqdltOo1mKP_jocu00fGm9ozfRO\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Versa H27 TG supports motherboards up to ATX, a tower CPU cooler with maximum height 160mm, and a dual expansion slot VGA of up to 310mm in length without front fan. The hidden drive bays can house up to five 2.5&rdquo; or three 2.5&rdquo; &amp; two 3.5&rdquo; storage devices at same time.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>AIO Liquid Cooling Compatible</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/i0hrfJXhqqMcw4zCEaah3MRWSPSMZ5XTIxGLyNx2ofEKFwULtT5TYVLCvzN0sQ85i97sbz9Y7ZwnhTKX2JA6Sux_JsLK8uFlliKCAgvjm0qtStgxsnTJpg9D-2VT2_0C6_p8p9cp\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supporting all types of AIO liquid cooling solutions, the Versa H27 TG has the capability to accommodate up to a 360mm radiator at the front or the top and a 120mm radiator at the rear.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Optimized Ventilation</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/9QrcOEiAtuS0xOxwWwtHJw4uGuWCY1P1-chL84mKn2JDcoYjyJGGXHYas2e_g8WEHUAKhecdt2pare9gTbDQQvivxq6xxGB9jNLNu6_7cD_d6I2omW_SR-sKqKisa3YKukCeBf7e\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Standard equipped with a 120mm rear fan along with optional three 120mm intake fans as well as three 120mm or two 140mm exhaust fans provides efficient airflow for the system.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Versa H27 TG Fan Supporting List</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Q163nKJrJ0WvUFY71ptjTYhXtsiHH7ouMn_h4ez5CAK2zIck5Q3F75dGLmY77GuDNmc5FKqFNskFyREbtH-2rXbPsvhlF4nWPecliFOYQsZynMw-XXRFt_S1UBATTXiEd2C8hRGS\" /><br />\r\nVersa H27 TG Radiator Supporting List</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/Zq6EGHVkX7MgQYR0YOUORuUIi7Sv1CKmjB9jibp7u6pLAWOcd8P7e5mK1e-O7YlD43o_Tr2tRAH1g8GdqmnRP_IYbEfV3nopYOsMzioMEYKLyJclaDw328qWO8_VR8RfTmtAp8_I\" /></p>', '<h2>Additional Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Model</td>\r\n			<td>Thermaltake Versa H27</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Case Type</td>\r\n			<td>Mid Tower</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Power Supply</td>\r\n			<td>Standard PS2 PSU (optional)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Supported Mainboard Type</td>\r\n			<td>ATX, Micro-ATX, Mini-ITX</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Graphics-card Length</td>\r\n			<td>310mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Radiator Support Front/Top/Rear</td>\r\n			<td>Front: 1 x 360mm, Top: 1 x 360mm, 1 x 280mm, Rear: 1 x 120mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Front Audio Port</td>\r\n			<td>1 x HD Audio</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Cooling Fan (Built-In)</td>\r\n			<td>1</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Cooling Fan (Optional)</td>\r\n			<td>6</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>CPU cooler height</td>\r\n			<td>160mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Front U