(693, 1, 2, 50, 3, 53, 65, 'Thermaltake View 21 (Tempered Glass Side Window) Mid Tower Gaming Desktop Case #CA-1I3-00M1WN-00', '<h2>Thermaltake View 21</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/4RXgT1LjpNswAnInYKnY9a2B_JoN-2cs8jiPCscKK4IO1Uj4f3DV3hevgqzETsBIognsIwOum2in7k6ilt7URjJJjv9KoC8TZp8FssgUJv3rZ51hs_Tbny6Iq_BTskdyTDatRY72\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>View 21 Tempered Glass Edition</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>ATX mid-tower chassis with dual 4mm thick tempered glass windows and one preinstalled 120mm fan.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Thermaltake View 21 Tempered Glass Edition Mid-Tower Chassis</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The View 21 Tempered Glass Edition mid-tower chassis features dual durable 4mm thick tempered glass windows (left &amp; right), one preinstalled 120mm rear fan with removable filters, full-length PSU cover and outstanding system ventilation. The View 21 TG supports the latest PC hardware and all high-end GPU solutions, guarantees on unparalleled expandability for high-end configurations and liquid cooling system to satisfy the market where users have opted for stylish PC chassis with advanced features and aesthetic appeal.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Tt LCS Certified</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tt LCS Certified is a Thermaltake exclusive certification applied to only products that pass the design and hardcore enthusiasts standards that a true LCS chassis should be held to. The Tt LCS certification was created so that we at Thermaltake can designate to all power users which chassis have been tested to be best compatible with extreme liquid cooling configurations to ensure you get the best performance from the best features and fitment.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Left and Right 4 mm Thick Tempered Glass Window Design</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The left and right 4 mm thick tempered glass windows guarantee the durability of the window; moreover, the enlarged window design permits users to fully display and admire all components of the liquid-cooling system. Show off your dedicated set in the subtlest manner!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Built-in PSU Cover</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The View 21 TG is equipped with a full-length PSU cover to hide those unsightly cables from view and give your build a sleek and tidy look, and what&rsquo;s more, a better airflow.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Supreme Hardware Support</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The View 21 TG comes with fully modular drive cages that provide the ease of installation/removal and maximize the interior space for custom cooling loop thanks to the design of a &ldquo;2+2&rdquo; HDD mounts inside the left side panel, and the two 2.5&rdquo;-compatible HDD slots in the PSU cover.<br />\r\nTwo 3.5&rdquo; and two 2.5&rdquo; HDD brackets included, so users are allowed to freely mount 2.5&rdquo; HDDs either on the wall of the PSU cover or vertically inside the left side panel to show off their HDDs.<br />\r\n3.5&rdquo; or 2.5&rdquo; HDD Drive Compatible</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Dust Reduction</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Super fine front filter, front panel filter, and bottom filter come with excellent protection and reduction against dirt and dust.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Supports High-End PCs with Outstanding Expandability</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The View 21 TG features its cable management with maximum 50mm in width, and supports up to a tower CPU cooler with maximum height 160mm, and a dual expansion slot VGA of up to 410mm in length without HDD rack. Moreover, the View 21 TG has the ability to accommodate multiple 3.5&rdquo;/2.5&rdquo; storage devices at the same time. Most importantly, the hidden drive bay design guarantees expandability for more liquid cooling components.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Advanced Ventilation</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The View 21 TG delivers advanced cooling performance for DIY/AIO liquid cooling and air cooling systems. With wide top-to-bottom side ventilation grills, the View 21 TG dissipates heat properly with (1) rear built-in 120mm fan, and it includes options for up to (5) 120mm fans.<br />\r\n*The image is for reference only; one rear fan is included, and the application of Riing Fan Series is optional.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Model - Thermaltake View 21, Case Type - Mid Tower, Supported Mainboard Type - ATX, Micro-ATX, Mini-ITX, Front USB port - 2 x USB3.0, Front Audio Port - 1 x HD Audio, 3.5 - 2, 2.5 - 2, Expansion Card Slots - 7, Cooling Fan (Built-In) - 1, Cooling Fan (Optional) - 6, Radiator Support Front/Top/Rear - Front: 1 x 360mm, 1 x 280mm, Rear: 1 x 120mm, Power Supply Type - Standard PS2 PSU (optional), Graphics-card Length - 410mm, CPU cooler height - 160mm, Transparent Side Window - Yes (Full Window), Body Color - Black, Body Dimensions (H x W x D) - 492 x 208 x 471mm, Weight - 8.05Kg, Others - PSU length limitation: 220mm, 4mm Tempered Glass x 2, Material&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;: SPCC, Specialty - Tempered Glass Side Window Mid Tower Gaming Desktop Case, Part No - CA-1I3-00M1WN-00, Warranty - 1 year</p>', '<h2>Additional Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Model</td>\r\n			<td>Thermaltake View 21</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Case Type</td>\r\n			<td>Mid Tower</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Power Supply</td>\r\n			<td>Standard PS2 PSU (optional)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Supported Mainboard Type</td>\r\n			<td>ATX, Micro-ATX, Mini-ITX</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Graphics-card Length</td>\r\n			<td>410mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Radiator Support Front/Top/Rear</td>\r\n			<td>Front: 1 x 360mm, 1 x 280mm, Rear: 1 x 120mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Front Audio Port</td>\r\n			<td>1 x HD Audio</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Cooling Fan (Built-In)</td>\r\n			<td>1</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Cooling Fan (Optional)</td>\r\n			<td>6</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>CPU cooler height</td>\r\n			<td>160mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Front USB port</td>\r\n			<td>2 x USB3.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Expansion Slots</td>\r\n			<td>7</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r