(696, 1, 2, 50, 3, 53, 65, 'Thermaltake Versa J22 TG RGB Tempered Glass Mid Tower Black Desktop Case # CA-1L5-00M1WN-01', '<h2>Thermaltake Versa J22 Tempered Glass RGB Edition</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/c4uJ6LPkoRBDMeRxf_-AXr0aQkbzwBavapczcgXE_b1peeGT7vzUS69xGfry0yjne6D5CSd4kpW6wP5xVfL39DP4gON8uu62kmgoylbkNiVS9YDMk50mRZZyUGnlK5xsVPAlcbNv\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ATX mid-tower chassis with one tempered glass window and three preinstalled 120mm RGB fans.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Thermaltake Versa J22 Tempered Glass RGB Edition Mid-Tower Chassis</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Versa J22 is designed for the PC builder who wants a classic look and 5.25&rdquo; bay support, but wants amazing cooling performance and tempered glass as well. The special RGB edition of the J22 comes with 3 built-in 120mm 12V RGB fans that are dual-mode controllable either via the I/O port RGB button or the synchronization with enthusiasts&rsquo; favorite RGB capable motherboard brands, including Asus, Gigabyte, MSI, ASRock, and Biostar.&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe J22 is a standard mid-tower with ATX support, but it also boasts a suite of premium features that make it the most outstanding standard case you&rsquo;ve seen</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/P2RY4L0M4y7oIv1MvwFvmstQ-NqAux9I_zlIXa2F7jFxkZWSv92seFygJTirozu6sEmoS4e-E0tZL5yEqlyq_6-8b32gmpUypgRgBRGZpYCOu5eKeWZunn4mpwHzQak2zux5bcmx\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>3 Built-in 120mm 12V RGB Fans</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Versa J22 TG RGB is preinstalled with three 120mm 12V RGB fans that can be controlled using a simple interface built into the I/O panel that cycles through three different lighting modes and a range of different color options.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/tzxHrORXIcNf7oHraHsuvQMfdusRBblix2kSDBEyKeO2gkz7lJXZEYyBzwy9d5Lv0j8q-DvCt_X3tkKDhVKOJ-2RHhAtzSQM2jcfs8JwA6Gr174XPJnW6RY8wewt3WKEx6DDfN8x\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ewE78QFWPcrlBpp73I0GEOGOUIswFEwBz1tAYeLJJ5UcJKIfu1rbvAZOp3ZSI6A2bGnbLFs7P_lXtycrom_cf_r5r3NTLQns3Xqoj3pTni92BboG9NeVhaFQqzTJFde8DkKIBXNZ\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Sync with Motherboard RGB Software</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Designed to synchronize with ASUS Aura Sync, GIGABYTE RGB Fusion, MSI Mystic Light Sync, ASRock RGB LED, and BIOSTAR Vivid LED DJ, the included 12V RGB front fans allow you to control the lighting modes through your motherboard software. Visit the support page for motherboard information or to download the software:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/oZBZkcRp0koNSmUTARu1Af2bgJGOp5lP_T21sC623NB27hXoeDzmbL4jW9Hua_o5PKl2SZHhkyQg4fnB3KYQ5MK4fNdNsHZ6IVlmOwynZwU5xemJE4scbptaaFxZjACuzR212gUm\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Built-in RGB Switch Board</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to the built-in RGB switch board, Versa J22 TG RGB is able to deliver the ultimate RGB lighting customization through the I/O port RGB button or the synchronization with ASUS Aura Sync, GIGABYTE RGB Fusion, MSI Mystic Light Sync, ASRock RGB LED, and BIOSTAR Vivid DJ-enabled motherboards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/kYrnBbGfdpa-rY0RFvuwqy3pJM_NMn2TlzC7xvqicJC-LkVeBtmnWjpwrquPRy8cX_oZ2QbOCtjCZZ_n5ZeA-5toWS5QO8vshehGCFTKqRNyNT_IyhX90OtaPnqZnzF6Yv38_nU8\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Built-in PSU Cover</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipped with a full-length PSU cover with a ventilated design to improve airflow and hide those unsightly cables.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/htqxBJ34lBSEVE5oiIVYtiPyi2eRFcBUTtlQ_p-OGcAn9bzOSgb1eKK4FPyNdN01YZVs2CfPPZVoCieEC8ypk_15CDUqoiD1mC3AF_ijgmKKeAv_BixuQQ5vu4mGDUBb4BDcuNoC\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Tempered Glass Window</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The tempered glass window on the side of the J22 is built to be more durable and scratch resistant than older acrylic panels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/Tkd22tgwgMbrRXbTqdjaGTXR58I26W5wPOYPPe8uGBwEQKV8ouc7OdzE78aKZjC2bCzNMiwWstfIclqUKXdgNLiD8E2T9x72cH7uZbciCet6nGSlkd8DAubJ3yJBEhZ22eWgBuRt\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Tool-Free Installation</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The included 2.5&rdquo;/3.2&rdquo; tool-less drive caddies can be installed in a number of locations around the chassis, including under the PSU shroud, behind the motherboard tray and on top of the PSU cover.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3.5&rdquo; or 2.5&rdquo; HDD Drive Compatible</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/tKFK6RhuLBvSjL_m_w3stAJI7PIPyGBSZCZBdjkJInjntYNaY6r-Wma52NTF48Ea-KDfI0uJRYnURxyDJlsJdMgUHm01DWqojxR0K62RgEj2Olt3_71vGhT1_5DR02X95dIKVVg8\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/8cwDp6RiFhDlQsxztbZZQjPwZbRtRU1QoEEYGJhxm04trDirmO5e2kHhTH_N12Mw8TeosiIhNbuozsAojVw-g0a_GTa0pU626LN07rkifaGykTd0oCHGUJku0EsK_MTZnh8ImlAd\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Superior Hardware Support</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Versa J22 has outstanding expandability with support for a tower CPU cooler with maximum height 160mm, a dual expansion slot VGA of up to 310mm in length, and a power supply with length of up to 170mm. The front panel also includes one 5.25&rdquo; bay for optical drive support</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/t3h37miSGod_4FuTwccJzQdek6p-laRzViSTcQYwBBq2aOJF72i1lGu3bBUPY7fVnpTIXUloRBJjmLAx35d_SL_-hrjkHoAYW5sYvZpROI8WkpWUnK3NzcJb1Tx73fE4oX019fMd\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Excellent Cooling Capability</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Optimized for excellent cooling capability with one 120mm exhaust fan preinstalled. The case is able to house up to dual 140mm or three 120mm front fans, up to 2x 140mm fans on top, and a radiator size up to 280mm at the same time to allow users to build a complete high-end system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/28v6BKTZ09BUCKUssLoUwTZyO4Fhk1xVGaTuNtZxVazjMfRUAIq1A1ENtHI2WOH6nmuCzw0TvC9zZrE4QBL0GLyWByOxqF0FQKmoMAuGbzSxSoX3TbSw30ZYdpIuk0e58389uMeq\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Modern, Sleek Styling</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The perforated front provides ample airflow to fans mounted behind the front panel, while keeping dust and air particles out of the system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/OdQxKHBztRZ1yJRHrHdv0mVTtzhmqKnUYvlAVdxPdXbgOZpJezfgMQu75oA_hKuOi1sFSKl5FnpgeAyl8mhZndENrwOtaJawXTrmAWuXRtkj-I7-HQow9rWTvkj14TMXWfSIzhmi\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Handy I/O Ports</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>One 3.0 and two 2.0 USB ports on top-front panel to grant direct access when needed. As well as a standard 5.25&rdquo; bay for optical drives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/mOGGnTv58rh_nr2yuwAR-UIFpzjxHMbg29zWGQd6DxNUoykVdQ15QrZ5Z7ZYrXBZguzEQXIzG68zbUty25JgdiHe7wgp65JulE-HIRlKQDPrP7xRcepX7erDIg09MRVIzVpb-aSU\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Radiator Supporting List</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/stjYSTPv1PcKJqu9UNDykqePjJGV7scF9H8I5jUHJ9qmMEDS4-4FXZZlymMeoTCtLlyIz1mgYDbXKTn12LieI1_T3faoq5ZCHXOQ3QeDtHsDY37b6zxc_MDGgvykNx1CfYQlo4ex\" /><br />\r\nFan Supporting List</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/eIS1p97O3YrtlZLi-8A8z0c-E1-J_7B_irOlwh__EmB3TZC-MZYbJpdgPeRg4kXDsV7F903X53K--0JGB_CBQG0B1yUMCK7Ys5RT74-_ALh4yTiAtyHrWoYtkqY2buOLftNq4qIA\" /></p>', '<h2>Additional Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Model</td>\r\n			<td>Thermaltake Versa J22 TG RGB</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Case Type</td>\r\n			<td>Mid Tower</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Power Supply</td>\r\n			<td>Standard PS2 PSU (optional)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Supported Mainboard Type</td>\r\n			<td>ATX, Micro-ATX, Mini-ITX</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Graphics-card Length</td>\r\n			<td>310mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Radiator Support Front/Top/Rear</td>\r\n			<td>Front: 1 x 240mm, 1 x 280mm, Top: 1 x 240mm, Rear: 1 x 120mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Front Audio Port</td>\r\n			<td>1 x HD Audio</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Cooling Fan (Built-In)</td>\r\n			<td>3</td>\r\n		</