(699, 1, 2, 50, 3, 53, 65, 'Thermaltake Commander C35 TG ARGB Tempered Glass Mid Tower Black Gaming Desktop Case # CA-1N6-00M1WN-00', '<h2>Thermaltake Commander C35 TG ARGB</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-w5FaWoLweuSprGcNbTNiqgABSDxoe2dmVJGP6l5Httm4neoQVeY1bheC3zvs-U5IXC2vlZxKe_l2MLC05vcNP0sQdklklmEim_vGgz-2xhrd0CB-3qJ7QtLTsNnaTea0dFo6e69\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mid-tower case with tempered glass side panel and two preinstalled 200mm 5V ARGB front fans and one 120mm standard rear fan, supporting up to ATX MB.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Commander C 35</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dual 200MM ARGB Fans Tempered Glass</li>\r\n	<li>ATX Mid-Tower Chassis</li>\r\n	<li>Two Built-in 200mm 5V ARGB Front FansExcellent Cooling Capability with 2-Way Radiator Mounting up to 360mmBuilt-in ARGB Switch Board for Different Lighting ModesGaming Design, Mesh Front PanelRiser GPU Support BracketBuilt-in Power Cover4mm Tempered Glass Side PanelSuperior Hardware SupportSupports both ARGB Color Synchronization with ASUS, MSI, GIGABYTE, and ASRock Motherboards, and a RGB color selection button via the I/O PortI/O Port Supports Dual USB 3.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Dual Built-in 200mm 5V ARGB Case Fans</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Preinstalled with two 200mm 5V ARGB front fans featuring hydraulic bearing, 9 addressable LEDs and 16.8 million-color illumination to guarantee high airflow and custom system designs to show off your PC design skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>One Click, Switching The Mode</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The 5V ARGB fans can be controlled using a simple interface built into the I/O panel that cycles through 7 different lighting modes and a range of different color options.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Tt LCS Certified</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tt LCS Certified is a Thermaltake exclusive certification applied to only products that pass the design and hardcore enthusiasts standards that a true LCS chassis should be held to. The Tt LCS certification was created so that we at Thermaltake can designate to all power users which chassis have been tested to be best compatible with extreme liquid cooling configurations to ensure you get the best performance from the best features and fitment.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Sync with Motherboard RGB Software</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Designed to synchronize with ASUS Aura Sync, GIGABYTE RGB Fusion, MSI Mystic Light Sync and ASRock Polychrome. It supports motherboards that have a 5V addressable RGB header, allowing you to control the lights directly from the above-mentioned software without installing any extra lighting software or controllers. For more details, please visit ASUS, GIGABYTE, MSI and ASRock official websites.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Angular, Mesh Front Panel</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Expanded from the gaming spirit of the classic Xaser VI chassis, the uniquely X shape design full mesh panel optimized airflow. With its modern design and high performance, it is the best choice for both gamers and enthusiasts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Riser GPU Support Bracket</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Specially designed for dual GPU placement options, Commander C Series has the support for vertical graphic card layout with dual PCI-E slots design. Integrated riser GPU support bracket not only prevents the graphic card from sagging, but also helps to reduce the weight on the motherboard PCI-E slots.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Built-in PSU Cover</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipped with a PSU cover with a ventilated design to improve airflow and hide those unsightly cables.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Seamless Tempered Glass Panel</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The tempered glass side panel of the Commander C35 TG ARGB is built to be more durable and scratch resistant than older acrylic panels.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Superior Hardware Support</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Commander C35 TG ARGB has outstanding expandability with support for a tower CPU cooler with maximum height 180mm, a dual expansion slot VGA of up to 310mm in length with reservoir, and a power supply with length of up to 200mm.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Handy I/O Ports</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual 3.0 USB ports on top-front panel to grant direct access when needed. As well as an ARGB button for controlling 7 lighting modes of ARGB fans.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Model - Thermaltake Commander C35 TG ARGB, Case Type - Mid Tower, Supported Mainboard Type - ATX, Micro-ATX, Mini-ITX, Front USB port - 2 x USB3.0, Front Audio Port - 1 x HD Audio, 3.5 - 3, 2.5 - 2, Cooling Fan (Built-In) - 3, Cooling Fan (Optional) - 3, Radiator Support Front/Top/Rear - Front: 1 x 360mm, 1 x 280mm, Top: 1 x 240mm, 1 x 280mm, Rear: 1 x 120mm, Power Supply - Standard PS2 PSU (optional), Expansion Slots - 9 (7+2), VGA Card Compatibility (Maximum) - 310mm(With reservoir) 410mm(Without reservoir), CPU cooler height - 180mm, Transparent Side Window - Yes, Body Color - Black, Body Dimensions (H x W x D) - 462 x 233 x 531mm, Weight - 7.84Kg, Others - Side Panel: 4mm Tempered Glass x 1, Material: SPCC, RGB Switch x 1, PSU length limitation: 200mm, VGA width limitation(Vertically): 45mm, VGA height limitation: 110mm, RAM height limitation: 35mm (With 140mm radiator series) 50mm (With 120mm radiator series), Specialty - Gaming Desktop Case, Dual 200MM ARGB Fans Tempered Glass, ATX Mid-Tower Chassis, Dual Built-in 200mm 5V ARGB Case Fans, 4mm Tempered Glass Side Panel, Riser GPU Support Bracket, Built-in ARGB Switch Board for Different Lighting Modes, Excellent Cooling Capability with 2-Way Radiator Mounting up to 360mm, Gaming Design, Mesh Front Panel, Built-in Power Cover, Sync with Motherboard RGB Software, Built-in PSU Cover, Part No - CA-1N6-00M1WN-00, Warranty - 1 year</p>', '<h2>Additional Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Model</td>\r\n			<td>Thermaltake Commander C35 TG ARGB</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Case Type</td>\r\n			<td>Mid Tower</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Power Supply</td>\r\n			<td>Standard PS2 PSU (optio