(732, 1, 2, 49, 3, 53, 65, 'Thermaltake Water 3.0 240 ARGB Sync Edition CPU Cooler # CL-W233-PL12SW-A', '<h2>Thermaltake Water 3.0 240 ARGB Sync Edition</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>All-in-one 240mm liquid cooler with PWM fan that supports 5V RGB capable motherboards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/7HlAmyzInrPoIjOj_phEmE6ycvFRWhAoxg5PF-C5z9EgfbN8HU52PgTC0WPWEyfY8NG75AWVwrf5I4-8dEnD6NNfFMBgIfqyi64J10zkF5r8T1gT_EsgKFcL5mCS10oJcAJ9h6aX\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>WATER 3.0 ARGB 240&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Water 3.0 ARGB Sync CPU cooler, is an all-in-one cooling solution that is available in either 120mm, 240mm or 360mm variants. Able to provide an alternative cooling solution to standard air cooling, the Water 3.0 is a perfect fit for achieving higher performance in any system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s also a fantastic choice for those that can&rsquo;t get enough RGB lighting in their build; thanks to the included Pure ARGB 5 volt radiator fans, switching between different lighting effects and colour options has never looked this good.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>KEEPING COOL UNDER PRESSURE&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to optimizing PC performance, keeping your components cool should always be a priority. A CPU is the beating heart of any gaming system, and is always going to require the best cooling hardware in order to help support it. By utilizing an all-in-one liquid cooler such as the Water 3.0, the truest potential of your CPU can be fully realized.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Over-clocking is something that can only be achieved through a liquid cooling solution, allowing your system to achieve even higher performance targets. You can also rest easy knowing that when you use the Water 3.0, it will help in eliminating any risks of damage to your hardware that can sometimes cause due to inefficient cooling be applied from stock cooling methods.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>HASSLE-FREE INSTALLATION&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Implementing a new cooler is easier than you think. The Water 3.0 is both simple and straightforward when it comes to implementing it into your system. A lot of the work is already done for you, with thermal paste already pre-applied on the base of the waterblock to allow for stress free placement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to a simple and efficient water cooling solution, the Water 3.0 is by far the easiest and most user friendly. No maintenance required or coolant to periodically top up, unlike traditional cooling setups. Once you&rsquo;ve integrated the Water 3.0 into your system, you can set it and forget it.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>JUST BE COOL</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Making sure your components always receive the right amount of cooling, should always be a priority when it comes to deciding on which case to house your system. Which is why we&rsquo;ve endeavored to give you plenty of cooling options in the View 27.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you&rsquo;re just starting out and want to play it safe by just utilising fan cooling, or you&rsquo;re a bit more adventurous and want to try your hand at a liquid cooling loop; the View 27 offers plenty of space for any and all of these cooling solutions and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>NEED AN ASSIST?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Sometimes, it helps to have someone who can offer a helping hand if the worst should happen. At Thermaltake, we&rsquo;re dedicated in providing quality products and even higher quality customer service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the Water 3.0, we&rsquo;ve endeavoured to offer a full three years product warranty in order to give you the confidence when deciding to purchase with us. By having a dedicated tech support team based in Australia, we understand how to properly serve our local customers and are able to deliver timely support and assistance.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>EVERYTHING UNDER YOUR CONTROL</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Speaking of addressable LED fans, you&rsquo;ll have total freedom when it comes to personalisation. With over 16.8 million colours to choose from, the only limitation is your own imagination. Through either software or hardware controls, you can switch between different lighting modes for some truly dazzling effects, to help draw even more attention to your system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As an added benefit, any compatible motherboard software can be synced with the included ARGB fans, allowing for consistent colours across all of your components. If you prefer, you can also use the included fan controller for easy manual adjustments and tweaks. (Only supports motherboard with 5V header)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Model - Thermaltake Water 3.0 240 ARGB Sync Edition, Cooler Type - Liquid CPU Cooler, Dimension (Heat Sink/Radiator) - 270 x 120 x 27mm (Radiator), Fan Dimensions - 120 x 120 x 25mm, Fan Speed - PWM 500-1500 R.P.M (2510-4PIN), Fan Air Flow - 56.45 CFM, Fan Air Pressure - 1.59 mm-H2O, Fan Noise Level - 25.8 dB-A, LED Color - ARGB, Supported Socket - Intel LGA 2066/20113/2011/1366/1156/1155/1151/1150, AMD TR4/AM4/FM2/FM1/AM3+/AM3/AM2+/AM2, Speciality - Pure 12 ARGB Sync Radiator Fan, Sync with Motherboard RGB Software, Switch LED Modes with ARGB Controller, High Efficiency Radiator, High Performance Waterblock, High Quality Pump, ARGB Sync Edition comes with two 120 mm fan with a large surface radiator, high performance waterblock and pump for ultimate CPU cooling, The built-in Pure ARGB fan features compression blades, hydraulic bearing, and 16.8 million colors LEDs that is ready to sync with 5V RGB capable motherboards from Asus, Gigabyte, MSI and AsRock, Others - Water Block Material: Copper, Pump Motor Speed: 3600 RPM, Pump Rated Voltage: 12 V &amp; 5V, Pump Power Input: 12V - 3.9 W, 5V - 1.06 W, Fan Rated Voltage: 12 V &amp; 5V, Fan Power Input: 12V - 1.44 W, 5V - 1.6W (one fan), LED Control: ARGB controller or 5V addressable RGB header on motherboard, Tube Length: 326mm, Tube Material: Rubber, Weight: 1230gm, Part No - CL-W233-PL12SW-A, Warranty - 1 year</p>', '<h2>Additional Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Model</td>\r\n			<td>Thermaltake Water 3.0 240 ARGB Sync Edition</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Cooler Type</td>\r\n			<td>Liquid CPU Cooler</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Supported Socket</td>\r\n			<td>Intel LGA 2066/20113/2011/1366/1156/1155/1151/1150, AMD TR4/AM4/FM2/FM1/AM3+/AM3/AM2+/AM2</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fan Speed</td>\r\n			<td>PWM 500-1500 R.P.M (2510-4PIN)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>LED Color</td>\r\n			<td>ARGB</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fan Air Pressure</td>\r\n			<td>1.59 mm-H2O</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fan Noise Level</td>\r\n			<td>25.8 dB-A</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fan Air Flow</td>\r\n			<td>56.45 CFM</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fan Dimensions</td>\r\n			<td>120 x 120 x 25mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Part No</td>\r\n			<td>CL-W233-PL12SW-A</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Dimension (Heat Sink/Radiator)</td>\r\n			<td>270 x 120 x 27mm (Radiator)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Specialty</td>\r\n			<td>Pure 12 ARGB Sync Radiator Fan, Sync with Motherboard RGB Software, Switch LED Modes with ARGB Controller, High Efficiency Radiator, High Performance Waterblock, High Quality Pump, ARGB Sync Edition comes with two 120 mm fan with a large surface radiator, high performance waterblock and pump for ultimate CPU cooling, The built-in Pure ARGB fan features compression blades, hydraulic bearing, and 16.8 million colors LEDs that is ready to sync with 5V RGB capable motherboards from Asus, Gigabyte, MSI and AsRock</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Others</td>\r\n			<td>Water Block Material: Copper, Pump Motor Speed: 3600 RPM, Pump Rated Voltage: 12 V &amp; 5V, Pump Power Input: 12V - 3.9 W, 5V - 1.06 W, Fan Rated Voltage: 12 V &amp; 5V, Fan Power Input: 12V - 1.44 W, 5V - 1.6W (one fan), LED Control: ARGB controller or 5V addressable RGB header on motherboard, Tube Length: 326mm, Tube Material: Rubber, Weight: 1230gm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Warranty</td>\r\n			<td>1 year</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', 11720, 'Thermaltake Water 3.0 240 ARGB', 'piece', 1, '0', 0, 'BDT', 'public/product_image/Thermaltake-Water-ARGB-Sync-Edition-CPU-Cooler-CL-W-PL-SW-A732.jpg', 0, 1, '2020-08-17 03:06:06', '2020-08-17 03:06:06');
