(737, 1, 2, 49, 3, 56, 65, 'Corsair Hydro Series H45 Liquid CPU Cooler #CW-9060028-WW', '<h2>Corsair Hydro Series H45<br />\r\nLiquid CPU Cooler</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Hydro Series H45 makes your PC run cooler and quieter when you replace your CPU&rsquo;s stock heatsink.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/dhAUtkGSaJkrku0n5gOWRuXqTEva5a5fX1D9_diwCUfeD737CAbNd1wWSnLRdi5aSztvJI4EGoiaGcs6N51cnMUVWY-Ba7kvRaQQuFFeoh_MOa4PIGhKKzNrKPXxrctN4jyV8Zed\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>MAKE THE MOVE TO LIQUID</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Your PC will run cooler and quieter when you replace your CPU&rsquo;s standard heatsink with a Hydro Series H45. Installation is straightforward: if you can get to the back of your PC&rsquo;s motherboard, you can install an H45. All you&rsquo;ll need is a screwdriver. The compact components and flexible tubing make Hydro Series H45 easy to install even if you&rsquo;re cramped for space. It allows you to improve your CPU&rsquo;s cooling efficiency even in most compact cases &mdash; as long as your case has a 120mm fan mount near the CPU, the H45 will probably fit.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>SELF-CONTAINED COOLING SYSTEM</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Serious liquid cooling for high-performance CPUs no longer means dealing with complex plumbing. Hydro Series H60 comes pre-filled, and never needs refilling or priming.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/qvSjPHd2GAc8mZBiBe3HG16JMEDI81LsImuLWiQ4zSQ90DsUv4Cu5CemMKxFv8VBkC8501FFt-IYJg-YGEM8J0wQizAzv69pnX5xTPnLTQlUIGukrizR0cVIIrQUuKeTm_ZjGoxs\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>LOW PERMEABILITY RUBBER TOOLING</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Minimal coolant evaporation helps ensure long life, and the resilient rubber offers both high flexibility and excellent leak protection.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>LOW-PROFILE PUMP</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The pump unit provides high-speed circulation without taking a lot of space. This makes installation easier, and helps improve your case&rsquo;s airflow.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>COPPER COLD PLATE WITH PRE-APPLIED THERMAL COMPOUND</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Copper has better thermal conductivity for more efficient heat transfer to the manifold. Pre-applied thermal compound lets you save a potentially messy installation step.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Radiator Dimensions: 168.5mm x 120mm x 71mm<br />\r\nFan Dimensions: 120mm x 25mm<br />\r\nFan Speed: 2300 RPM&nbsp;<br />\r\nFan Airflow: 94 CFM<br />\r\nNoise Level: 31 dBA<br />\r\nFan Static Pressure: 3.65 mm-H2O</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Model - Corsair Hydro Series H45, Cooler Type - Liquid CPU Cooler, Dimension (Heat Sink/Radiator) - 168.5 x 120 x 71mm (Radiator), Fan Dimensions - 120 x 25mm, Fan Speed - 2300 RPM, Fan Air Flow - 94 CFM, Fan Air Pressure - 3.65 mm-H2O, Fan Noise Level - 31 dBA, Supported Socket - Intel 115x, Intel 2011/2066, AMD AM3/AM2, AMD AM4, Speciality - MAKE THE MOVE TO LIQUID, SELF-CONTAINED COOLING SYSTEM, LOW PERMEABILITY RUBBER TOOLING, LOW-PROFILE PUMP, COPPER COLD PLATE WITH PRE-APPLIED THERMAL COMPOUND, Hydro Series H45 Liquid CPU Cooler, Others - Cold Plate Material: Copper, Radiator Material: Aluminum, PWM: YES, Number of Fans: 1, Radiator Size: 120mm, Part No - CW-9060028-WW, Warranty - 2 Year</p>', '<h2>Additional Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Model</td>\r\n			<td>Corsair Hydro Series H45</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Cooler Type</td>\r\n			<td>Liquid CPU Cooler</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Supported Socket</td>\r\n			<td>Intel 115x, Intel 2011/2066, AMD AM3/AM2, AMD AM4</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fan Speed</td>\r\n			<td>2300 RPM</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fan Air Pressure</td>\r\n			<td>3.65 mm-H2O</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fan Noise Level</td>\r\n			<td>31 dBA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fan Air Flow</td>\r\n			<td>94 CFM</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fan Dimensions</td>\r\n			<td>120 x 25mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Part No</td>\r\n			<td>CW-9060028-WW</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Dimension (Heat Sink/Radiator)</td>\r\n			<td>168.5 x 120 x 71mm (Radiator)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Specialty</td>\r\n			<td>MAKE THE MOVE TO LIQUID, SELF-CONTAINED COOLING SYSTEM, LOW PERMEABILITY RUBBER TOOLING, LOW-PROFILE PUMP, COPPER COLD PLATE WITH PRE-APPLIED THERMAL COMPOUND, Hydro Series H45 Liquid CPU Cooler</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Others</td>\r\n			<td>Cold Plate Material: Copper, Radiator Material: Aluminum, PWM: YES, Number of Fans: 1, Radiator Size: 120mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Warranty</td>\r\n			<td>2 year</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', 5400, 'Corsair Hydro Series H45 Liquid', 'piece', 1, '0', 0, 'BDT', 'public/product_image/Corsair-Hydro-Series-H-Liquid-CPU-Cooler-CW-WW737.jpg', 0, 1, '2020-08-17 03:30:10', '2020-08-17 03:30:10'),
(738, 1, 2, 49, 3, 56, 65, 'Corsair Hydro Series H5 SF Low-Profile Liquid CPU Cooler #CW-9060023-WW', '<h2>Corsair Hydro Series H5 SF<br />\r\nLow-Profile Liquid CPU Cooler</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/xjV0x348hLNQKAYZZg0laLbTWkxbpbPZLGsPkHrh7Z_HBw1yhDnuVVzz7o-vIS3LXxpBtim_6xlY_rWzRleNSkDHGMwdUa_3l-Z8ZNskpFBKghlo0BEXUgNgdgLDy5nqxabxX5UC\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Hydro Series H5 SF is a low profile liquid CPU cooler that provides efficient cooling for small form factor cases. The integrated high-pressure blower fan provides powerful and quiet liquid cooling.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>QUIET, POWERFUL LOW-PROFILE LIQUID CPU COOLING FOR HIGH-PERFORMANCE MINI-ITX PCS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Hydro Series H5 SF is a low profile liquid CPU cooler that provides efficient cooling for small form factor Mini-ITX systems. Building a small form factor system shouldn&#39;t have to mean compromising on processor speed, and with the H5 SF you can provide reliable cooling for your system&#39;s high performance CPU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/jxoqcGdQlz8pp-mMOIR0Lakr40QwIKuQWzxvARmTP5dSlfxU3xpjK6TXM7MbdhDyRO484gtI83iqUX5fMiNK8AnCGB6w5trPJLdiQ1fhWAL6AZ9PKPSGTvf9pf-gwNPeIJH2qsrt\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>LOTS OF COOLING POWER IN A SMALL SIZE</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The H5 SF solves the problem of providing effective liquid cooling for high performance CPUs in cases where a full-sized Hydro Series liquid CPU cooler won&#39;t fit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/0HhbwC_ewx3-6kMwwnFlCqDuE688OBqPytmZS7TZvUPUrK5ggq0RvZ__bqDq1iJOhi_bgH4uVKsQZgcJ5R1uJPkLeQmiJLlEIEz2ibsAWSrOJsRIicQTIMwye97F0KbjoD6P9wi-\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>WORKS WITH CORSAIR AIR240, 250D, AND 380T CHASSIS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The H5 SF was originally developed for the Corsair Bulldog living room gaming system, but it also works great in other Corsair small form factor chassis with dual rear 80mm fan mounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/EPqlyhvBziraw2m7ppYWMfLe_CP7twjAsksmC6NkK63oORz4qApBEVJpZu7ssyuXYhjx0bTcB1V3NFNpQKdrVK7_s-bzubDamU617FEpmO_-DpVvADKv3Sg2rAzP7LFojh7zr7gK\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>UNIQUE COOLING SYSTEM DESIGN</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>It has a pump assembly with a copper coldplate and flexible, low permeability tubing, just like our larger Hydro Series models. They&#39;re matched with a one-piece blower which cools the circulated liquid by drawing cool air from the inside of your PC and exhausting it outside the case. So, in addition to keeping your CPU cool, the H5 SF provides additional cooling for the motherboard and other components by constantly pulling cool air across them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/yKF8LVNDRCTA0TuF_1jjAquvhNOKbcZcJK7z7LFqtnKVIgV2oFAJshrVxguAns5Wo8LptmjmqbEn8cVuUA1p4ikqLE4Tu9w53z6zAkWV3NAvlUAtG9AAuPaAYDAd2VyKoDROoU3-\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>PREMIUM COMPONENTS FOR HIGH PERFORMANCE AND EASIER INSTALLATION</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The low permeability tubing helps ensure long life, and the flexible design makes installation easier in tight spaces. The cold plate uses copper for its excellent heat transfer properties, and pre-applied thermal compound saves you time and mess during installation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/cEDH_hz1Fm1MgHBy9NueJxxQTYza9ylJqL7W5RO1_dJGcMyfOCO5Ih2zLzRqHqg4b-DULLtOPFvo5YVu_SJjmkU9YN1nUhKDJ4ASD0amoZERtZLNMjICFp2zyfsaxzOcjDlVyNTG\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Model - Corsair Hydro Series H5 SF, Cooler Type - Liquid CPU Cooler, Speciality - low profile liquid CPU cooler that provides efficient cooling for small form factor cases, The integrated high-pressure blower fan provides powerful and quiet liquid cooling, QUIET, POWERFUL LOW-PROFILE LIQUID CPU COOLING FOR HIGH-PERFORMANCE MINI-ITX PCS, LOTS OF COOLING POWER IN A SMALL SIZE, WORKS WITH 