(898, 1, 2, 51, 3, 53, 65, 'Thermaltake Challenger Edge Pro RGB Lighting Black Keyboard # KB-CPR-PLBRUS-01', '<h2><br />\r\nThermaltake Challenger Edge Pro RGB Lighting</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/UmrRAg1eN_b4zcFqfHV5YsdYa-0OFAuAMiymiQ73ghfjUzwfsEXIYqEc6LPGEMPPxQrjUiCw_-zhrBsijgD3wKg_zux78YmAl1SdC-JFGewOHqHJEJa_g_TBE9pJDTJ91W8E4b5B\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Challenger Edge Pro RGB gaming keyboard is Cherry MX keycap compatible, and comes in a unique floating keycap design with a sleek minimalistic aluminum finish. It delivers per key backlighting of 16.8 million true RGB colors and comes with 13 dynamic lighting effects for a truly enhanced gaming atmosphere. Packed with features including: 5 pre-configured FPS1, FPS2, MMO, MOBA and RTS lighting zones, anti-ghosting, n-key rollover, detachable wrist rest and dedicated volume &amp; mute controls, it offers maximum customization with ultimate simplicity to suit all your gaming needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>16.8 M TRUE RGB ILLUMINATION WITH 13 LIGHTING EFFECTS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/ii45X11sJMZT11GhwMFQWKafe_-bIWouWgfECTTNo7t1bnXSSOZcK91Ou0ozPfpiG25g7CUSgTRpb6Gtzdhp6sMYIC5spzdu_RKd5gCd66WCdAFjOIummRTG4jWbaZ7qM-7QJhSK\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stunning 16.8 million RGB color illumination under keys provides the brightest visibility and eye-catching style for your gaming session. Take it a step further and choose between 13 different lighting effect settings coupled with 4 individual levels of brightness and lighting speed to provide maximum color customization tailored your style.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>FLOATING KEYCAP DESIGN WITH ALUMINUM FINISH</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/FpO138BEyGq_6RPKHEMxgCzuOLGQxUChF4RIWgvjoZdSVKTqfN1GbljHMZvix_Sp0Tgagieu4kFaUfsytOLlEDRj0e2UkRsPDaPPSMu3QMc2mf1iG55KsQR3BChjoXRfZpWGMBMO\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Floating keycap construction provides the Challenger Edge Pro RGB with a modern and sleek aesthetic appearance desired by gamers, coupled with a premium grade aluminum finish for that ultra-modern design effect. The use of a floating keycap construction not only looks stunning but also provides easy cleaning between the gaps for each individual key for enhanced durability.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>PRE-CONFIGURED 5 LIGHTING ZONES</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/OuqPLinSAYb9t4zYHxL2sxIXCIzsmzytZht52IFZkJ0d7zk2yN4cPRdhwPN2pNrvX7hzYJvWkJP8j1vEzI05l-9MI1CKsfNLbQNivUqJOkARNsfx-dCPh6nTF7ZDfm61C18kUKww\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/RYJN75bIAJyfCJcTg_s8A7dnHYSslB1Qr9PB_Ma3NF6FdozQerDD9bf6gLMCoWMalP_iB2XjoCK0e_ePJYRz9NhczwRUYIr72niDCUdLyXINj7vEWwMg8kIxVaSNJqFwiU5_Uxe5\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/aE9HN5un9n4Opr4KCl7vk2gtX1rxU7hUw2CyYFSuGFz101AGj4JGxs-cBFMUtxsn2sj_LNwFPnS-RJCnokqKTdwSuY9-PsMSP0IhH-qguBdm0KiwpnJB6zNyj4hUEuI_OvOp9U5F\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>5 pre-configured game genre lighting zone illuminations: FPS1, FPS2, MMO, MOBA and RTS for that all-important gaming advantage during gameplay.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>PLUNGER SWITCH</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/Hp9TT5pRUSIiz6AaFySON_nH2ho5LiKUtgOHmMSzxx-W3kZPyb93xgAUgkPBjPqFaajcDoKk2R78sB-MPPqqTdFVNtyzcztBgYe7S-2UqBTfOSyW_e_Esu1oGnz-QOXdHAPXml-0\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Challenger Edge Pro RGB gaming keyboard features TteSPORTS Plunger keys that are specially tuned to deliver a superior tactile response and performance profile similar to a mechanical keyboard. The new Plunger keys at full height deliver a full 2.4mm pre-travel distance with 50g &plusmn; 5g actuation force.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>19 KEY ANTI-GHOSTING WITH 6-KEY ROLLOVER</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/FTs94LAojiaTBbEPYYlqJlZ7H-gogO-eKJyX4aOdlEEdCZ1T_lqQdtiLn4FpU9zDaIGnvYlex7VwD9yf3VwOnymXxeforcGMYN41A8zADoun-YEVn4GpTP9NTOU5jrZJB_WAX__7\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Allows 6 key combinations (Q, A, Z, W, S, X, E, D, C, B, SPACE, TAB, ALT+L or V, CTRL+L or F, SHIFT+L &amp; 4 directional keys) to be registered simultaneously. Inclusion of disable windows key and full signal lock key prevents accidental activation of the Windows Start function and enables full lock of the keyboard whilst not in use for easier cleaning and unintentional command.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>MULTIMEDIA SHORTCUT KEYS WITH DEDICATED MUTE AND VOLUME CONTROLS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/sTQwqxcIaWxrwN8CVnyJKiLKFfg6f_0JEh4SmKJ4Z2ZgaBbCJq73PsyKWs3gi5xDQFgoy2iP0VpJHa4GddCGnXmUjhMLqcHTbHD21VvY0N1hY1FyITQKGqk116N9p6RZ9H9sWMBb\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Take control of your sound on-the-fly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>DETACHABLE WRIST REST</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Play longer and in optimal positioning with the detachable wrist rest for enhanced ergonomic comfort during long and intense gaming sessions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>MACRO AND PROFILE SUPPORT</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/PFVRc_ofkwO9xi6gs7wwXCf2lKifO3fI4yvxsagnW75dSYbILd93M_rQlPNsmHFIJxBwhqa-nFEh3A0ItiFUA7SQlDQIg8m61eKUJxOdgEwMleWbrzjnLwlO_g7EgQyX1L9BC7ay\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Customize with the Tt eSPORTS gaming software and take control of the most expansive set of macros and personalization options. Give yourself full control to program multiple keystrokes to a single key, change backlighting effects with intuitive keyboard commands or set with easy to quick launch custom game profiles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Model - Thermaltake Challenger Edge Pro RGB Lighting, Series - Gaming, Style &amp; Size - Regular Big, Type - Gaming Keyboard, Interface - USB, Language (English) - Yes, Language - English, Mouse, Touchpad - Keyboard only, Mechanical (Key) - No, Lighting - Yes, Dimensions (WxHxD) - 428 x 199 x 42mm, Weight - 1034gm, Specialty - The Challenger Edge Pro RGB gaming keyboard is Cherry MX keycap compatible, and comes in a unique floating keycap design with a sleek minimal